Package com.pb.sawdust.tabledata.basic

Provides implementations and extensions of various data table interfaces.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasicDataColumn<T>
    The BasicDataColumn class provides a simple implementation of the DataColumn interface.
    BasicDataRow
    The BasicDataRow class provides a simple implementation of the DataRow interface.
    BasicDataSet
    The BasicDataSet class provides a simple implementation of the DataSet interface.
    BasicTableIndex<I>
    The BasicTable class provides a simple implementation of the TableIndex interface.
    BasicTableKey<K>
    The BasicTableKey class provides a simple implementation of the TableKey interface.
    CoercedDataTable
    The CoercedDataTable class is a data table which wraps another data table, but modifying the data types of the underlying table's columns.
    ColumnDataTable
    The ColumnDataTable class provides a "column-based" implementation of the DataTable interface.
    DigestTableIndex<I>
    The BasicDigestTableIndex class provides a TableIndex implementation which uses message digests for its unique indices.
    DigestTableIndex.ByteDigest
    The ByteDigest class is a simple wrapper for the digests returned by the MessageDigest class.
    FixedSizeDataTable
    The FixedSizeDataTable class a data table wrapper which cannot have rows or columns added or removed.
    ListDataTable
    The ListDataTable class provides an implementation of the DataTable interface backed by a List.
    OrderedDataTable
    The OrderedDataTable ...
    PieceWiseDataTable
    The PieceWiseDataTable class provides a data table which consists of a (non-contiguous) selection of rows from another data table.
    ReadOnlyWrappedDataTable
    The ReadOnlyWrappedDataTable class provides a data table wrapper whose contents cannot be modified.
    RowDataTable
    The RowDataTable class provides a "row-based" implementation of the DataTable interface.
    SimpleTableIndex<I>
    The SimpleTableIndex provides a table index built on a single column from the data table.
    WrappedDataRow
    The WrappedDataRow class provides a DataRow implementation which wraps another data row.
    WrappedDataTable
    The WrappedDataTable class provides a DataTable implementation which wraps another data table.
